« The C Programming Language » also known as « The K&R » from the names
Kerningham and Ritchie, who wrote it.

In this book which explains the C programming language, there are programming 
exercises to experiment each new concept. I decided to make them all.


Here you can download the pdf version of this book:
http://net.pku.edu.cn/%7Ecourse/cs101/2008/resource/The_C_Programming_Language.pdf

